data.description: UNBEATABLE VIEWS at Ladera View! Step into a two-story paradise boasting 5 bedrooms, 3 full baths, and top-tier upgrades. Upon entrance, luxurious 24-inch polished porcelain tiles pave the way. The elegant gas fireplace creates a cozy ambiance, perfect for family gatherings. The expansive primary suite offers a walk-in shower with custom tiles stretching to the ceiling. The kitchen is a chef's dream. From your covered patio, immerse yourself in captivating views of the rolling hills. Crafted with precision and detail, this home is a testament to exquisite living. A visual treat you can't afford to miss! Veteran only Assumable 2.25% VA loan 607k for Veterans only. Need to have full eligibilty of $726,000.
